"      * The entire assessment should be performed at baseline and every 12 to 24 months in patients who are receiving ERT and have achieved therapeutic goals (DEXA should be performed every 24 months in these patients); the entire assessment also should be performed at the time of dosage change or the development of a significant complication.",
